$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
set_damage_chance

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_damage_chance -  This method sets the percentage of the damage which is done to the object which will be carried through.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_damage_chance(int number)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^number%^RESET%^ - the new damage chance

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/basic/condition.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets the percentage of the damage which is done to the
object which will be carried through.


Use the following chart to set the damage chance. 
